{{obsolete}}

{{flavour|It affects your evasion (+5 to EV)}}

'''Evasion''' is a [[brand]] that [[ranged weapons]] may have which grants the player +5 [[EV]]. Although this may help you survive battles with other ranged monsters and can prove useful should you need to flee, it is generally preferable to have a brand that helps you deal extra damage in combat.

==History==
The evasion brand was removed in [[0.19]]

